e target user\'s gender is male/female/other), and `up.gender IS NULL` is only t
rue for incomplete profiles which are already filtered out by `up.is_complete = 
1`. So users with `preferred_gender = \'all\'` would see NO recommendations. Thi
s is a critical bug.\n\nAlso, `gender` in `CreateProfileDto` has enum values `ma
